- data/raw/ippl/src/Particle/ParticleBase.h : ParticleBase — core particle base class that manages particle attributes and positions.
- data/raw/ippl/src/Particle/ParticleBase.h : ParticleAttribute<T> — class used to define specific attributes of particles.
- data/raw/ippl/src/Particle/ParticleBase.h : addAttribute — method to add custom attributes to the `ParticleBase` instance.
- data/raw/ippl/src/Particle/ParticleBase.h : particle_position_type — type for storing particle positions, shared with velocity attribute in the example.
- data/raw/ippl/src/Particle/ParticleBase.h : ParticleSpatialLayout<double, 3> — layout class used for spatial distribution of particles in 3D space.

